thread.title: BRIEF-Taiming Assurance Broker to pay cash dividend of T$3.2 per share to shareholders for 2017

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Taiming Assurance Broker to pay cash dividend of T$3.2 per share to shareholders for 2017

organizations.name: reuters) - taiming assurance broker co ltd

text:
Feb 26 (Reuters) - Taiming Assurance Broker Co Ltd
* Says it will use undistributed profit to pay cash dividend of T$3.2 per share to shareholders for 2017
* Says it will pay cash dividend of T$75.8 million in total
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/uQBs6c
